{"tid":926115,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"烏大龜(最近)","createTime":"2018-12-03T08:17:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T09:01:02.000Z","uid":219183,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4136281f4cb12dbfa84ea2b0162c1b075d481586","tid":926115,"uid":219183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T08:17:12.000Z","msg":"烏大龜是站着計數而穿保安衫的唯一的人。他身材不高大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；青白臉色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，皺紋間時常夾些傷痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；一部亂蓬蓬的花白的鬍子。穿的雖然是保安衫，可是又髒又破，似乎十多年沒有補，也沒有洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。他對人說話，總是滿口MK behaviour，教人半懂不懂的。因爲他係龜，別人便從不文集上的「小喇叭烏大龜」這半懂不懂的話裏，替他取下一個綽號，叫作烏大龜。烏大龜一上線，所有連登的人便都看著他笑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有的叫道，「烏大龜，你怎麼又回來校園台了！」他不回答，對admin說，「溫兩碗酒，要一本教科書。」便排出九題數。他們又故意的高聲嚷道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，「你一定又被抄登巴打趕出來了！」烏大龜睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你被眾巴打恥笑，吊著打。」烏大龜便漲紅了臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，額上的青筋條條綻出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，爭辯道，「退出不能算趕&hellip;&hellip;退出！&hellip;&hellip;IQ135的ENTJ，還會被趕麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「Entering university is MK behaviour」，什麼「中化考得好都是狗公」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽人家背地裏談論，烏大龜原來也讀過書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但終於沒有學位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，又不會擦鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；於是愈過愈窮，弄到要做保安了。幸而算得一手好數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，便替人家計計數，換一杯精飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。可惜他又有一樣壞脾氣，便是好吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嬾含<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。坐不到幾天，便連人和題目紙計算器，一齊失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。如是幾次，叫他計數的人也沒有了。烏大龜沒有法，便免不了偶然做些MK behaviour<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。但他在校園台裏，品行卻比別人都好，就是從不拖欠；<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然間或沒有題目，暫時記在粉板上，但不出一日，定然還清，從粉板上拭去了烏大龜的名字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n烏大龜計過半條數，漲紅的臉色漸漸復了原<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，旁人便又問道，「烏大龜，你當眞認識數學麼？」烏大龜看着問他的人，顯出不屑置辯的神氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。他們便接着說道，「你怎的連半個學位也撈不到呢？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />烏大龜立刻顯出頹唐不安模樣，臉上籠上了一層灰色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，嘴裏說些話；這回可是全是MK behaviours 之類，一些不懂了。在這時候，衆人也都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在這些時候，我可以附和着笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，admin是決不責備的。而且admin見了烏大龜，也每每這樣問他，引人發笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。烏大龜自己知道不能和他們談天，便只好向廢青說話。有一回對我說道，「你讀過書麼？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我略略點一點頭。他說，「讀過書，&hellip;&hellip;我便考你一考。這道中四數學題，怎樣算的？」我想，保安一樣的人，也配考我麼？便回過臉去，不再理會。烏大龜等了許久，很懇切的說道，「不能算罷？&hellip;&hellip;我教給你，記着！這些算術應該記着。將來做保安的時候，消磨時間要用。」我暗想我和保安的等級還很遠呢，而且我們保安也從不計數消磨時間；又好笑，又不耐煩，嬾嬾的答他道<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，「誰要你教，不是歐拉公式麼？」烏大龜顯出極高興的樣子，將兩個指頭的長指甲敲着櫃臺，點頭說，「對呀對呀！&hellip;&hellip;這道M2 數學題的解法，你知道麼？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我愈不耐煩了，努着嘴走遠。烏大龜剛用指甲蘸了酒，想在櫃上計數，見我毫不熱心，便又歎一口氣，顯出極惋惜的樣子。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有一天，admin正在慢慢的派膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，取下粉板，忽然說，「烏大龜長久沒有來了。還欠十九條數呢！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我纔也覺得他的確長久沒有來了。一個吹水的人說道，「他怎麼會來？&hellip;&hellip;他打折了腿了。」admin說，「哦！」「他總仍舊去偷。這一回，是自己發昏，竟串到CUHKBanters家裏去了。他家的學位，偷得的麼？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「後來怎麼樣？」「怎麼樣？先寫服辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，後來是打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，打了大半夜，再打折了腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」「後來呢？」「後來打折了腿了。」「打折了怎樣呢？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「怎樣？&hellip;&hellip;誰曉得？許是死了。」admin也不再問，仍然慢慢的派他的膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自此以後，又長久沒有看見孔乙己。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我到現在終於沒有見&mdash;&mdash;大約孔乙己的確死了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471a622e8f731061bcbf365036012f187ae246ec","tid":926115,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T08:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自此以後，又長久沒有看見<span style=\"color: red;\">孔乙己</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我到現在終於沒有見&mdash;&mdash;大約<span style=\"color: red;\">孔乙己</span>的確死了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n專業啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebef5a1c434419e0daf85246b02e99df1819a22","tid":926115,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T08:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aae04bad2cb49a07d0dcabd131ac8560a012f55","tid":926115,"uid":198998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T08:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edcbaafaaca623b95dd45cf358bee1827cd7883d","tid":926115,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T08:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08e8f8da3845ae109a0fbfd1f8537e371783694","tid":926115,"uid":219183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:01:02.000Z","msg":"repo link: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/926162/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/926162/page/1</a>"}]}